.07805361,-0.055479,0.03738619,-0.06180733,-0.07941769,0.01953008,-0.02582259,-0.06501101,0.0659134,0.05438901,-0.06081577,0.0273735,0.07830048,-0.04312993,0.04538607,-0.02175402,-0.04586701,0.07549526,0.03407555,-0.04799579,-0.07779603,0.08741048,0.0399878,0.04619493,0.05307779,-0.03521479,-0.04451872,0.06037198,-0.04757603,0.10967501,0.01011095,-0.04103028,-0.01440218,-0.02064906,-0.08386617,-0.09420527,0.07885423,-0.06166214,-0.07684539,0.04441408,0.02426199,0.06138977,0.02415178],"last_embed":{"hash":"1k0kcyp","tokens":444}}},"text":null,"length":0,"last_read":{"hash":"1k0kcyp","at":1774775687051},"key":"docs/science/function/2.md#导数入门","lines":[31,523],"size":11153,"outlinks":[{"title":"x_{0}, x_{0} + \\delta)$ 有定义，且极限\r\n\r\n$$\r\n\\lim\\limits_{\\Delta x \\to 0^{+}} \\dfrac{f(x_{0} + \\Delta x) - f(x_{0})}{\\Delta x}\r\n$$\r\n\r\n存在，那么称这个极限为 $f$ 在 $x_{0}$ 的**右导数**，记作 $f'_{+}(x_{0})$。\r\n\r\n函数在 $x_{0}$ 可导的充要条件是它在 $x_{0}$ 的左导数和右导数存在且相等，即 $f$ 在点 $x_{0}$ 连续。（更加严谨的是，可导 ⇒ 连续，连续 ⇏ 可导）。\r\n\r\n如果函数 $f$ 在区间 $I$ 内的每一点都可导，且在端点单侧可导，那么称 $f$ 在区间 $I$ 上可导。此时 $x \\mapsto f'(x), x \\in I$ 确定了一个函数，称为 $f$ 的**导函数**，简称**导数**，记作 $f'(x)$ 或 $\\dfrac{\\d f}{\\d x}(x)$。后一种符号由德国数学家莱布尼茨发明。\r\n\r\n### 切线问题\r\n\r\n![alt text","target":"image.avif","line":23},{"title":"alt text","target":"image-1.avif","line":395,"embedded":true},{"title":"alt text","target":"image-2.avif","line":456,"embedded":true},{"title":"alt text","target":"image-4.avif","line":482,"embedded":true}],"class_name":"SmartBlock","last_embed":{"hash":"1k0kcyp","at":1774775687051}},
